high_descs: Turn left and walk to face the space between the sinks.
Pick up the soap dispenser sitting between the sinks.
Turn left and move to face the sink on the left and the cabinet below it.
Open the cabinet door on the right, place the soap dispenser inside, and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the toilet.
Pick up the soap dispenser sitting on the toilet's water tank.
Turn around and head left towards the sink and cabinet on the left.
Open the right cabinet door, place the soap dispenser inside, and close the door.
anns.task_desc: put the soap dispensers in the cabinet under the sink.

high_descs: turn and walk to the middle of the bathroom sinks
grab the soap off of the bathroom sink counter
back up a bit to face the left side bathroom sink
open the cabinet below on the right and put the soap in there
walk over to the toilet
grab the soap off the top of the toilet
walk back over to the same bathroom cabinet
place the soap inside the cabinet to the right of the other soap
anns.task_desc: place the two soaps inside the bathroom cabinet

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the two sinks.
Pick up the soap from the center of the two sinks.
Turn around, then right to face the left sink.
Open the cabinet below the sink and place the soap inside and close it.
Turn left, then right to face the toilet.
Pick up the soap from the top of the toilet tank.
Turn around then walk left to be in front of the sink.
Put the soap inside the cabinet under the sink and close it.
anns.task_desc: Put soap pumps in the cabinet under the left sink.
